            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>(S) In Christi nomine. Breve pro fucturis et modernis temporibus
                        securitate ac firmitate ad memoria abenda vel retinenda qualiter in loco in
                        via plubica et vocitatur a <placeName>Lupo Inpiso</placeName> prope <rs
                            key="#Baptismal_churches">ecclesia plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches">Sancti *** et Sancti Iohanni
                            Batista</orgName> da <placeName key="#Baptismal_churches"
                            ref="#places/270">Tabbiano</placeName> presentia <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum ominum</rs> corum nomina supter
                        leguntur veniens <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/221">Dodo</persName>
                        gratia Dei uius <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/124"
                            >Sancte Rosellensis</orgName> umilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        per fuste et pergamina quas in suis detinebat manibus nomine ac censum
                        perexolvendu dare videor tibi <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/219"
                            >Stefano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartiolomei Apostoli</orgName> de sito loco <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/281">Curte Mainberti et vocitatur a
                            Sextinghe</placeName> idest medietate ex integram de omne reditu et
                        debitu illo de <rs key="#Villages/settlements">villis</rs> illis que dicitur
                            <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/281">Sextinghe et de Curte
                            Mainberti</placeName> et <placeName key="#Decima">Valle
                            Petrosora</placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/297"
                            >Prugnano</placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/344">Vico
                            Caldane</placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/345"
                            >Cesi</placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/346"
                            >Collicle</placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima"
                                ref="#places/348"><placeName key="#Decima"
                                    ref="#places/347">Tile</placeName></placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima"
                            >Ranoclaria</placeName>, <placeName key="#Decima" ref="#places/292"
                            >Perita</placeName> quantas singulis ominibus in predictis villis illis
                        quod de eorum <rs key="#Decima">decimatione</rs> debiti sunt ad retdendu a
                        domo <rs key="#Mother_churches">etpiscopatui</rs> nostro beati Sancti
                        Laurentii etpiscopatu Rosellensis tam <rs key="#Cereals">labore</rs> quam et
                            <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> et de <rs key="#Animals">bestiis</rs> tam <rs
                            key="#Cows">vitolis</rs> quam et de <rs key="#Pigs">porci</rs> et de <rs
                            key="#Sheep">pecoribus</rs> et iumentis ex <rs key="#Wildfowl"
                            >volatilibus</rs> seo qualibet rem <rs key="#Hay/fodder">fenu</rs>
                        <rs key="#Silver">argentu</rs> seu ex omnia suprascriptis ominibus de
                        predictis villis et in eorum finibus da <placeName key="#Rivers"
                            >Teupasscio</placeName> usque a <placeName key="#Rivers"
                            >Brona</placeName> consuetudo fui a redendu exepto et antepono illa
                        decima detine qui ego per <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >libello</rs> dedi <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Teutius"
                                >Teutii</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> et <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Ursus">Urso</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> nam illa alia omnia et in omnibus
                        suprascripta medietate sicu <persName><name ref="Rainerius"
                            >Raineri</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Rofredus"
                                >Roffredi</name></persName> per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellum</rs> abui et sicu
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/210">Andreas</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> per <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >libellum</rs> abuit. Item ego qui supra <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/221">Dodo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> per fuste quas in suis detineba manibus
                        nomine ac censu et perexolvendu dare videor tibi <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/219">Stefano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de suprascripto <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/126"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> de
                            Sextinghe</orgName> idest de omne reditu et debito illo <rs
                            key="#Decima">decimatione</rs> de omnibus aliis <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis et de cassinis</rs> seo de <rs
                            key="#Casalini/fundamenta">casalinis</rs> et de sortis et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> seo
                        rebus de quantu suprascripte <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et monastero
                        Sancti Bartiolomei aquistato abet tam per <rs key="#Cartula">cartula</rs>
                        vel pro <rs key="#Oral_grants">investiscione</rs> quonquisito de <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Decima" ref="#places/348">Alma</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Decima" ref="#places/349"
                            >Blanculana</placeName> et <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Decima"
                            ref="#places/350">Caralle</placeName>, a <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Decima" ref="#places/321">Tatte</placeName>,
                            a.r<placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Decima" ref="#places/314"
                            >Ravi</placeName>, <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Decima"
                            ref="#places/270">Tabbiano</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/343">Prata</placeName> vel de
                        omnibus aliis terris et rebus qui suprascripto monasterio aquisito abet que
                        sunt pertinentibus decimatione fuerunt consuetudo ad redendu a domo <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">etpiscopatui</rs> nostro beati <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/124">Sancti Laurentii
                            etpiscopatui</orgName>
                        <placeName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#places/273">Rosellensis</placeName>
                        tam <rs key="#Cereals">labore</rs> quam et <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> et de
                            <rs key="#Animals">bestiis</rs> tam <rs key="#Cows">vitolis</rs> quam et
                        de <rs key="#Pigs">porci</rs> et de <rs key="#Sheep">pecoribus</rs> et
                        iumentis ex <rs key="#Wildfowl">volatilibus</rs> seo qualibet rem <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">fenu</rs>
                        <rs key="#Silver">argentu</rs> seo ex omnia suprascriptis ominibus de
                        predictis villis et in eorum finibus da Teupascio usque fluvio Brona
                        consuetudo fui ad retdendum. Tali ordine ut datmodum in tua qui supra
                        Stefano abbas et a.ttuos sucessores int potestate permaneant eas abendi
                        tenendi recolligiendi faciendi exinde de iam dicta decimatione quiquit
                        volueritis. Nisi tantu pro omni censu iustitia exinde mihi qui supra Dodo
                        episcopus vel a posterisque successoribus meis omnis singulos annos in mense
                        augusto censum nobis retdere debeatus a.ssuprascripto domui etpiscopatu
                        Sancti Laurentii pensione argentu solidos quattuor boni expendibilis quali
                        pre tempore currit per vos aut per misso vestro nobis vel a misso nostro aut
                        a ministeriale illu qui tempore abuerimus tantu. Et si a nos vobis etc omnia
                        qualiter supra legitur per singulos annos sic fuerit adinpleta et conservata
                        et nos vobis suprascripto redito et debito illa decimatione quas tibi dedi
                        retollere vel suptragere vel minuare quesierimus aut anplius vobis
                        superimposuerimus per quolibet ingenio spondeo ego qui supra Dodo episcopus
                        una cum posterisque successoribus meis componere vobis qui supra Stefano
                        abbas vel ad vestrisque successoribus tuis pena argentu obtimu libras
                        viginti. Hoc factu est in presentia <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Wido">Guidi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rufinus">Rofini</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Rodelandus">Rollandi</name></persName> germani filii
                        bone memorie <persName><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iudo">Hiudo</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Iudo">Hiudi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainerius/Sclavo">Raineri que
                            Sclavo</name></persName> vocatur filio bone memorie <persName><name
                                ref="Ildebrandus">Ildibrandi</name></persName> et reliquis plures.
                        Hoc factu est anno ab incarnatione Domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo
                        septuagesimo secundo decimo kalendas augusti indictione nona.</ab>
                        </div>
